name="Height Trait System"
type="mod"
version="1.0.0"
required_version="1.11+"
description="A mod that enhances the height trait mechanics in CK3.

This mod introduces a new height trait system, allowing for more depth in character design and interaction.

Features:
- Height variations influencing character interactions.
- Unique events related to height.
- Compatibility with other popular mods for CK3.

Enjoy a more immersive gameplay experience with diverse character traits!"